==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Great White Way
<hw>Great White Way</hw>. <def>Broadway, in New York City, in the
neighborhood chiefly occupied by theaters, as from about 30th Street to
about 50th Street; -- so called from its brilliant illumination at
night.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

